      "content": "it's just that the fear of going low is driving me crazy. if i follow the logic that i've had almost zero carbs, i'm basically not needing any extra insulin right now. wouldn't it be more logical to just skip it and prevent a crash entirely? i feel like you're being a bit too cautious and it's making me more anxious about the night.",
